Package main.java.daos

Class MenuDAO

java.lang.Object
main.java.daos.MenuDAO
All Implemented Interfaces:
DAOInterface<MenuItem>
public class MenuDAO extends Object implements DAOInterface<MenuItem>
MenuDAO is a Data Access Object (DAO) for managing MenuItem objects with CRUD Operations. It provides methods to interact with MenuItem data stored in Excel files. This class implements the DAOInterface.
Since:
24-Apr-2024

  • Method Details

    • readData

      public void readData()
      Reads data from Excel files and populates the menuItemList. If the files do not exist, it creates new Excel files. Handles IOException if encountered while reading or creating the files.
      Specified by:
      readData in interface DAOInterface<MenuItem>

    • saveData

      public void saveData()
      Saves the data from menuItemList to Excel files. If the files do not exist, it creates new ones. Handles IOException if encountered while writing the files.
      Specified by:
      saveData in interface DAOInterface<MenuItem>
